’s life total. The amount of life the player loses is determined as the triggered ability resolves.£10/1/2008: If multiple Quietus Spikes trigger at the same time, that player loses half their life when the first ability resolves, then loses half of the remainder when the next ability resolves, and so on. The player does not lose the same amount each time.£6/15/2010: In a Two-Headed Giant game, after combat damage is dealt, Quietus Spike looks at that player’s life total (which is the same as the team’s life total) when determining how much life the team will lose, which basically means the team’s life total is halved. Here’s an example of the math: The team has 19 life, so the player has 19 life. Quietus Spike causes the team to lose 10 life (19 divided by 2, rounded up). The team’s life total becomes 9 (19 minus 10).','A',NULL,'0.6','2.49','4.39',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'封喉刺',NULL,'Pointe de quiétude','Todesstoß-Nadel','Punta del Colpo di Grazia','滅消の杭','Espículo Quietus','Пика Успокоения','Estaca de quietud',NULL,'神器～武具',NULL,'Artefact : équipement','Artefakt — Ausrüstung','Artefatto — Equipaggiamento','アーティファクト ― 装備品','Artefato — Equipamento','Артефакт — Снаряжение','Artefacto — Equipo',NULL,'佩带此武具的生物具有死触异能。£每当佩带此武具的生物对牌手造成战斗伤害时，该牌手失去一半数量的生命，该数量小数点后进位。£佩带{3}',NULL,'La créature équipée a le contact mortel.£À chaque fois que la créature équipée inflige des blessures de combat à un joueur, ce joueur perd la moitié de ses points de vie, arrondie à l''unité supérieure.£Équipement {3}','Die ausgerüstete Kreatur hat Todesberührung.£Immer wenn die ausgerüstete Kreatur einem Spieler Kampfschaden zufügt, verliert dieser Spieler die Hälfte #_(aufgerundet)_# seiner Lebenspunkte.£Ausrüsten {3}','La creatura equipaggiata ha tocco letale.£Ogniqualvolta la creatura equipaggiata infligge danno da combattimento a un giocatore, quel giocatore perde metà dei suoi punti vita, arrotondati per eccesso.£Equipaggiare {3}','装備しているクリーチャーは接死を持つ。£装備しているクリーチャーがいずれかのプレイヤーに戦闘ダメージを与えるたび、そのプレイヤーは自分のライフの半分の点数（端数切り上げ）のライフを失う。£装備 {3}','A criatura equipada tem toque mortífero.£Toda vez que a criatura equipada causa dano de combate a um jogador, esse jogador perde metade de seus pontos de vida, arredondada para cima.£Equipar {3}','Снаряженное существо имеет Смертельное касание.£Каждый раз, когда снаряженное существо наносит боевые повреждения игроку, тот игрок теряет половину своих жизней с округлением в большую сторону.£Снарядить {3}','La criatura equipada tiene la habilidad de toque mortal.£Siempre que la criatura equipada haga daño de combate a un jugador, ese jugador pierde la mitad de su vida, redondeado hacia arriba.£Equipar {3}.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('174948','Rafiq of the Many','ALA','Legendary Creature — Human Knight','M','{1}{G}{W}{U}','4','3','3',NULL,'Exalted #_(Whenever a creature you control attacks alone, that creature gets +1/+1 until end of turn.)_#£Whenever a creature you control attacks alone, it gains double strike until end of turn.','#_Many sigils, one purpose._#',NULL,'Michael Komarck','185','4.086','£10/1/2008: If you declare exactly one creature as an attacker, each exalted ability on each permanent you control (including, perhaps, the attacking creature itself) will trigger. The bonuses are given to the attacking creature, not to the permanent with exalted. Ultimately, the attacking creature will wind up with +1/+1 for each of your exalted abilities.£10/1/2008: If you attack with multiple creatures, but then all but one are removed from combat, your exalted abilities won’t trigger.£10/1/2008: Some effects put creatures onto the battlefield attacking. Since those creatures were never declared as attackers, they’re ignored by exalted abilities. They won’t cause exalted abilities to trigger. If any exalted abilities have already triggered (because exactly one creature was declared as an attacker), those abilities will resolve as normal even though there may now be multiple attackers.£10/1/2008: Exalted abilities will resolve before blockers are declared.£10/1/2008: Exalted bonuses last until end of turn. If an effect creates an additional combat phase during your turn, a creature that attacked alone during the first combat phase will still have its exalted bonuses in that new phase. If a creature attacks alone during the second combat phase, all your exalted abilities will trigger again.£10/1/2008: In a Two-Headed Giant game, a creature “attacks alone” if it’s the only creature declared as an attacker by your entire team. If you control that attacking creature, your exalted abilities will trigger but your teammate’s exalted abilities won’t.','GWU (O)',NULL,'5','7','9.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'GWU','千印莱菲',NULL,'Rafiq aux Innombrables','Rafiq von den Vielen','Rafiq dei Molti','数多のラフィーク','Rafiq dos Muitos','Рафик Многомедальный','Rafiq de los Mil Sellos',NULL,'传奇生物～人类／骑士',NULL,'Créature légendaire : humain et chevalier','Legendäre Kreatur — Mensch, Ritter','Creatura Leggendaria — Cavaliere Umano','伝説のクリーチャー ― 人間・騎士','Criatura Lendária — Humano Cavaleiro','Легендарное Существо — Человек Рыцарь','Criatura legendaria — Caballero humano',NULL,'颂威 （每当一个由你操控的生物单独攻击时，该生物得+1/+1直到回合结束。）£每当一个由你操控的生物单独攻击时，它获得连击异能直到回合结束。',NULL,'Exaltation #_(À chaque fois qu''une créature que vous contrôlez attaque seule, cette créature gagne +1/+1 jusqu''à la fin du tour.)_#£À chaque fois qu''une créature que vous contrôlez attaque seule, elle acquiert la double initiative jusqu''à la fin du tour.','Edelmut #_(Immer wenn eine Kreatur, die du kontrollierst, alleine angreift, erhält diese Kreatur +1/+1 bis zum Ende des Zuges.)_#£Immer wenn eine Kreatur, die du kontrollierst, alleine angreift, erhält sie Doppelschlag bis zum Ende des Zuges.','Esaltato #_(Ogniqualvolta una creatura che controlli attacca da sola, prende +1/+1 fino alla fine del turno.)_#£Ogniqualvolta una creatura che controlli attacca da sola, ha doppio attacco fino alla 